    {
      "id": "q-promise",
      "navLabel": "Promise 组合方法",
      "question": "Promise.all / race / allSettled / any 区别？什么时候用？",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Promise 对象有三种状态："
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "pending"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "（进行中）、"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "fulfilled"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "（已成功）、"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "rejected"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "（已失败）；状态一旦落定（resolved）就不会再变。组合方法建立在 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "then"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 之上。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "Promise.all([a,b])"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：全部 "
          },
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "全部 fulfilled（成功）"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 才 resolve；任一项变成 rejected（失败）就立刻 reject。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "适合多接口强依赖、缺一不可的场景（如详情页需同时拉用户与权限）。注意：一个失败整批失败，要有降级或重试策略。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "Promise.race"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "："
          },
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "谁先 settled（落定）"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 就用谁（fulfilled 或 rejected 都算）。典型：超时封装 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "Promise.race([fetch, sleep(5000)])"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "Promise.allSettled"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：等全部 settled 才返回，每项是 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "{ status: 'fulfilled', value }"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 或 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "{ status: 'rejected', reason }"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "。适合批量上报、多源拉取——单项 rejected 也不拖垮整体。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "Promise.any"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "："
          },
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "第一个 fulfilled 即成功"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "；全部 rejected 才抛 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "AggregateError"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "。适合多 CDN/多镜像任意一个可用即可的兜底。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "示例："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "四个静态方法取向对照。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "const ps = [Promise.resolve(1), Promise.reject('e')]\n\nPromise.all(ps)        // 一挂全挂\nPromise.allSettled(ps) // 等全部落定，带 status\nPromise.race(ps)       // 谁先完成用谁（成功或失败）\nPromise.any(ps)        // 谁先成功用谁；全失败才 AggregateError"
          }
        ]
      ]
